## Seat Booking [/api/seat]

For booking seats. The POST method also create and return an unique Booking Identify Code.

### Book Seats [POST]

+ Request

        [
            "flightId": "abcdef",
            "seats": [
                {
                    "seatId": "15a"
                },
                {
                    "seatId": "16a"
                }
            ],
            "passengerId": "abc123"
        ]

+ Response 201

        {
            "bookingCode": "abczzz"
        }

+ Request

        [
            "flightId": "abcdef",
            "seats": [
                {
                    "seatId": "10a",
                }
            ]
        ]
+ Response 400

## Booking Infomation [/api/seat/{code}]

Return infomation about provided booking code.

+ Parameters
    + code (string) - booking identify code

### Infomation [GET]

+ Response 200

        [
            "flightId": "abcdef",
            "seats": [
                {
                    "seatId": "15a"
                },
                {
                    "seatId": "15a"
                }
            ],
            "passengerId": "abc123",
            "state": "1"
        ]